div1.p: United States of America Western District of Washington

I, JAMES C. DRAKE, Clerk of the Circuit Court of the United States, for the Western District of Washington, do hereby certify that the foregoing attached papers constitute the JUDGEMENT ROLL in the foregoing entitled cause, No. 1227 wherein In Re: Ham Hung Habeas Corpus
In Testimony Whereof, I have hereunto set my hand and affixed the Seal of said Circuit Court, this the 26 day of DEC A.D. 1911.
